@startuml threshold_mgmt_state

[*] --> ReceiveRequest : user action

ReceiveRequest --> ValidateInput

ValidateInput --> Error : invalid data
ValidateInput --> ProcessAction : valid data

ProcessAction --> CreateThreshold : create
ProcessAction --> UpdateThreshold : edit
ProcessAction --> DeleteThreshold : delete

CreateThreshold --> WriteToDB
UpdateThreshold --> WriteToDB
DeleteThreshold --> WriteToDB

WriteToDB --> Success
WriteToDB --> Error : db failure

Success --> [*]
Error --> [*]

@enduml